item.title: Please Help!
item.dc:creator: @quest_rs quest rs
item.description:
@quest_rs wrote:

Which IDE are you using? Most can highlight blocks of code inside braces for you, use that to check for missing or extra braces. Most IDEs also highlight the error, so that would be your best bet. I personally can’t be bothered into looking at random code from a file that huge as its a 50-50 chance.

If you do not have any IDE’s I suggest working with dr.java its fairly simple and great for people who make a lot of syntax errors.
